element.name: Park Life by AbbeyAckbar, Traditional Cache (1/1.5)

center.b:
A micro cache beside the pond in Santry Woods. Contains log only. Bring a pen with you.
It is hidden near the pond's edge (No need to swim! or enter the water whatsoever :) ).
A great spot to feed the ducks & swans from.

p.b: The park may be accessed from the Coolock Lane/Swords Raod junction where there is a car park just inside the entrance.
See gallery for opening/closing times of the park

ul.li:
2010-06-12T19:00:00Z : Found it by chatcar
Yes, today we got it! Thank you for the cache in a nice location.

2010-06-05T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by chatcar
Damned! Too early...park was closed!

2010-05-26T13:32:57Z : Enable Listing by AbbeyAckbar
This is the 3rd container i've placed for Park Life cache, so i've placed this one in a new location not far from its original spot. It is now secured to the tree so it won't go missing easily. The really weird thing is that as I was looking for a new hiding spot for the cache I found the 1st container that had gone missing! It had strayed quite a distance from its hiding place, but was positioned upright in a tree crevice with it's contents inside so I guess someone found it and placed it there!?! It was great to get the container back [:)] I wonder will I find the latest missing container a few months down the road...
